202
00:21:48,265 --> 00:21:51,101
Boy, you under arrest for murder.

203
00:21:53,520 --> 00:21:55,063
I interrupt?

204
00:21:56,607 --> 00:21:59,276
Well, I'm just about done.

205
00:22:09,161 --> 00:22:10,412
Hey...

206
00:22:10,996 --> 00:22:13,540
...how's that pretty gal of yours?

207
00:22:14,458 --> 00:22:16,752
